ConfigLoader - Class in com.jpmorgan.digital.helper
ConfigLoader is a helper class to load any config in section, tag and value format and convert it as a Map As per the implementation, config should be in seciton,tag and value format Tags allowed in config section tag value So a sample config can be as follows: <section> Section1 <tag> Tag1 <value>TagValue</value> </tag> <tag> Tag2 <value>TagValue</value> </tag> </section>
